SUMMARY:AI Developer Workshop (Raleigh) - Build AI Voice Agents
DESCRIPTION:Modern Web (Triangle)\nWe’re excited to partner with AICamp 
 for the hands-on workshop for the AI developers in Raleigh on April 9th.\n
 \nJoin SignalWire and AICamp for a hands-on session building AI Voice Agen
 ts for Modern Contact Center.\n\nThis hands-on workshop will build AI-driv
 en IVRs and contact center flows on SignalWire's control plane\, where sta
 te lives inside the call\, operations execute atomically\, and your code d
 efines logic instead of managing infrastructure. Learn how to build intell
 igent\, browser-based IVRs and contact center systems using SignalWire’s
  programmable unified communications stack.\n\nWhat You’ll Build:\n\\- A
 I\\-driven IVR with the SignalWire Python SDK\n\\- Omnichannel flows with 
 programmable voice and messaging\n\\- AI Agents with memory and context th
 at persist across interactions\\\, without external state management\n\\- 
 Deployment patterns that work at 10 calls and 10\\\,000 AI agents that fol
 low logic\\\, not 100 lines of prompting\n\\- Expect practical\\\, real\\-
 world talks from AI builders working deep in production AI systems\\.\n\n
 📅 Date: April 9th\, 2026\n🕔 Time: 5:00 PM \\~ 8:00 PM\n📍 Location
 : Nest Raleigh\n👉 Apply to build with us: https://bit.ly/4c6MtSo (The e
 vent is free\, pre-registration is required for admission. Seats are limit
 ed to 50 developers)\n\nFood and drink are provided. win an iPad 🎁 at t
 he end of the workshop!\nWe look forward to seeing you there!
