SUMMARY:Engineering with AI: Tools & Workflows for Next Gen Development Wo
 rkshop
DESCRIPTION:Modern Web (Triangle)\nJoin this immersive workshop to learn h
 ow modern engineering teams are integrating AI into everyday workflows. Th
 rough hands-on sessions\, you’ll explore proven frameworks and practical
  AI playbooks that make code reviews faster\, documentation smoother\, and
  planning more strategic.\n\nYou’ll leave with battle-tested frameworks\
 , real experience\, and a concrete plan to bring AI tools and automation i
 nto your daily dev process.\n\n**[This is a ticketed event. Seats are limi
 ted! Learn more here!](https://ai.thisdot.co/workshops)**\n\n**Use code MO
 DERNWEB at checkout for $50 tickets!**
